  "1863430": {
    "name": "龙的传人：孤旅",
    "steam_appid": 1863430,
    "required_age": "16",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/b27c2aefad3a52fcfe7bdce5361cdb79.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=614 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/b27c2aefad3a52fcfe7bdce5361cdb79.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/b27c2aefad3a52fcfe7bdce5361cdb79.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br>解放饱受摧残的世界：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/daeb41907b4e0af875151a0bb29562eb.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/daeb41907b4e0af875151a0bb29562eb.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/daeb41907b4e0af875151a0bb29562eb.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>在《Dragonkin: The Banished》中，你将沉浸于被龙血腐蚀的世界，邪恶生物从地底深处涌现。选择一个传奇英雄职业，肩负单一使命：追猎并消灭龙族生物。每场战斗都将你一步步引向最终目标——寻觅并铲除龙族领主。<br><br>联机共赴 Dragonkin 冒险<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/07adf1a70f943762f53d2ca2103a0b24.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/07adf1a70f943762f53d2ca2103a0b24.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/07adf1a70f943762f53d2ca2103a0b24.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>与好友在最多支持4人的在线合作模式中，共同体验龙裔冒险之旅。从踏入蒙特斯凯尔城到最终战役，整个龙裔冒险全程支持合作游玩。任务间隙，蒙特斯凯尔城将成为你的据点，在此可与其他玩家会合。每位玩家都肩负着建设城市的使。<br><br>四位猎龙英雄待命：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/fa5ae9dc5e63b76df91d88221cccae32.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/fa5ae9dc5e63b76df91d88221cccae32.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/fa5ae9dc5e63b76df91d88221cccae32.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>每位英雄都已练就了各自对抗巨龙的本领和战斗技巧。随着冒险推进，你的角色、装备、幼龙以及祖先网格都将不断成长进化。<br><br>追踪者：作为氏族顶尖猎手，她以猎物淬炼技艺，改良武器库。凡逃过她箭矢、利刃或陷阱的怪物，终将倒在她调制的毒药之下。<br><br>蛮族战士：如今他已拥有龙族血统，半人半兽之身，超凡力量与冰霜之力，融入他的传奇怒火，足以击败最强敌手。<br><br>神谕者：蓝龙之血改造了她，她能够精准运用电龙之力，借助神谕视野将其威力放大。<br><br>圣骑士：历经战斗的磨炼，他挥舞火焰长枪技艺超群。对永恒者的坚定信仰与不屈意志，使他免受龙族腐蚀，成为驱散黑暗的永恒之光！<br><br>独特升级机制：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/ed27eada37b97a6082f176f66dfd9ba9.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/ed27eada37b97a6082f176f66dfd9ba9.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/ed27eada37b97a6082f176f66dfd9ba9.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>探索祖先网格——全新系统助你将角色蜕变为拥有独特力量的传奇战士。战斗中获取技能作为战利品，结合众多增益效果在网格系统内进行战略布局。优化每个技能槽以提升实力。每位英雄拥有专属网格，可衍生出海量技能与增益组合。<br><br>待探索的世界：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/f8992a80512c424f804175b88c0cef52.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/f8992a80512c424f804175b88c0cef52.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/f8992a80512c424f804175b88c0cef52.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>征战龙族生物，踏遍 Dragonkin 的广袤世界。<br>丛林、古老岛屿、毒沼、广袤平原、冰川、干旱火山……众多秘境静待你去探索。你的冒险将揭示这个世界的丰饶，每片土地都孕育着独特的文化与历史。在旅途中，你还会遭遇各具特色的怪物，它们各自拥有独特的能力和属性（冰、毒、火、电），其掉落的资源可用来强化你的英雄。<br><br>随冒险推进而发展起来的城市：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a6b18898914bfc2338694b9fd22c1868.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a6b18898914bfc2338694b9fd22c1868.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a6b18898914bfc2338694b9fd22c1868.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>群山环抱，远离龙族侵扰的秘境中矗立一座宏伟都市——人类最后的堡垒。城市会随你的决策和探索不断发展和演变。随着冒险推进，你可设定城市发展的优先级：升级建筑、接纳新居民、发掘新装备与服务设施，将这座避难所打造成人类真正的庇护所。<br><br>1.0 版本即将上线：<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/dcfc77697e23fabcf0b0c02589212f78.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/dcfc77697e23fabcf0b0c02589212f78.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/dcfc77697e23fabcf0b0c02589212f78.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>《Dragonkin: The Banished》1.0 版本即将推出，抢先体验阶段也将结束。1.0 正式版将带来完整剧情、全新 50 级的初始等级系统，以及全面升级的狩猎板。<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a74f38aba077e8320baad59b21170857.poster.avif?t=1772123399\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a74f38aba077e8320baad59b21170857.webm?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1863430/extras/a74f38aba077e8320baad59b21170857.mp4?t=1772123399\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
